<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>514</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jīn shēng zhù dìng rè xuè yào rán shāo dé dào ēn huì yī dìng yào huí bào
 wǒ bù zhī dào tài yáng hái shēng duō gāo wǒ zhǐ zhī dào zhǔ kuài huí lái le
 zhǔ xiàng nǐ yào zhǔ xiàng wǒ yào, fú yīn de zhǒng zi nǐ sā duō shǎo
 dì xiōng xiāng ài cháng wān xià yāo, zhí qū yé lù sā lěng guāng míng dà dào.</lyrics>
<title>jīn shēng zhù dìng 迦南514</title>
</song>